<emphasis id="8EDBEA9E2114C6208EC2FD3324D47AFA" bold="true" box="[189,442,741,767]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">Conservation Status</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BC10368C2114C6208EC2FCC224DB7B92" blockId="7.[189,1399,788,920]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">
We provisionally assess 
<taxonomicName id="7BAF4D0F2114C6208F97FCC2279D7B2B" authority="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao, 2022" authorityName="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao" authorityYear="2022" box="[488,755,788,814]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Aspleniaceae" genus="Asplenium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="danxiaense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="8EDBEA9E2114C6208F97FCC2279D7B2B" box="[488,755,788,814]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">Asplenium danxiaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="95E857E52114C6208C81FCC226337B2B" box="[766,861,788,814]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
as Critically Endangered based on criterion D of 
<bibRefCitation id="D83E4B7D2114C6208F7FFCE124F37B54" author="IUCN" box="[256,413,823,849]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" refId="ref4599" refString="IUCN. 2012. IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria: Version 3.1. Second edition. Gland, Switzerland. Available from https: // portals. iucn. org / library / node / 10315 [accessed 5 November 2021]." type="url" year="2012">IUCN (2012)</bibRefCitation>
. Only one population and fewer than 50 individuals of 
<taxonomicName id="7BAF4D0F2114C6208A40FCE121887B54" authority="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao, 2022" authorityName="Lin &amp; Guo &amp; Zhou &amp; Liao &amp; Mao" authorityYear="2022" box="[1087,1254,823,849]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Aspleniaceae" genus="Asplenium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="danxiaense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="8EDBEA9E2114C6208A40FCE121887B54" box="[1087,1254,823,849]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="169">A. danxiaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="95E857E52114C6208A92FCE120247B54" box="[1261,1354,823,849]" pageId="7" pageNumber="169" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
are known from Danxia mountain. It was not seen by one of us during separate expeditions to nearby sites on Danxia mountain.
</paragraph>
